<p>
	<lb n="1" style="text-align: left"/>svasti śrī
</p>
<p>
	<lb n="2" style="text-align: left"/>kōvicaiya-nanti-vikkirra<unclear>m</unclear>
	<lb n="3" break="no"/>ma-parumark<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>u</reg></choice> yāṇṭu patiṉēḻava
	<lb n="4" break="no"/>tu
</p>
<p>
	pal-kuṉrā-k-kōṭṭattu maṇṭaikuḷa-nā
	<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭṭu-c curaikkuḷattu-t toṟu-k-kōḷil
	<lb n="6"/>ppaṭṭ<unclear>ā</unclear>r nilam peṟṟ<choice><unclear>u</unclear><unclear>a</unclear></choice> nāyakar Ataṭ
	<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṭiyār makaṉār ceruvaliyār
</p> 

